    • sceneGraphRevision

      public javafx.beans.property.ReadOnlyIntegerProperty sceneGraphRevisionProperty
      Returns the property holding the revision number of the scene graph. refreshSceneGraph() method increments the revision by one each time it refreshes the scene graph.

      public javafx.beans.property.ReadOnlyIntegerProperty cssRevisionProperty
